# LOG


## 2021-01-10


Registered <f3lt.net> domain with namecheap.com

```
	Domain Registration 	f3lt.net	1 year	$ 10.98 
	ICANN Fe 					$ 0.18
	TOTAL						$ 11.16 
```


Set up a VPS on Linode -- 1GB Ram, 1CPU, Ubuntu 20.04.1 LTS


Added A Record in the DNS to point to server ip : 198.74.51.225

	`A	f3lt.net	198.74.51.225	1798`


Check to see if DNS is resolving to ip

```
	$ getent hosts f3lt.net
	# 198.74.51.225   f3lt.net
```


Created local (bare) git repo

	`/srv/git/repositories/f3lt.space.git`


Installed some stuff

```
	$ whoami
	# root
	$ apt update
	$ apt upgrade
	$ apt install docker tmux
```
